Hebron Technology Co., Ltd. Sponsors TCM Industry Summit









PR Newswire




Jun 14, 2017 7:30 AM EDT













 


















































 WENZHOU, China, June 14, 2017 / PRNewswire/ -- Hebron Technology Co., Ltd. (" Hebron" or the "Company") (Nasdaq: HEBT), a developer, manufacturer and installer of valves and pipe fittings for use in the pharmaceutical, biological, food and beverage, and other clean industries, today announced that it has attended and sponsored the inaugural traditional Chinese medicine ("TCM") Industry Development Summit (the "Summit") which took place June 11, 2017 in Foshan City, Guangdong Province, China. The Summit, organized by the China Association of Traditional Chinese Medicine (the "CATCM") with Hebron among the co-sponsors, drew more than 100 attendees from government agencies, leading research institutes and more than 78 enterprises. Mr. Anyuan Sun, Chairman and Chief Executive Officer of Hebron, delivered a speech at the Summit, highlighting the recent developments at the Company following its successful IPO in December 2016, including new product development, project updates and new corporate initiatives.   "We are proud to join the CATCM as one of organizers and sponsors of the Summit, which brought together TCM industry leaders and academics from both China and Japan and provided a great venue for showcasing Hebron as not only a developer, manufacturer and installer of valves and pipe fittings but also a holistic engineering solution provider for pharmaceutical and TCM companies," said Mr. Sun.  About Hebron Technology Co., Ltd.  



 








 































































 











